	  stepchild if we\'re not careful.

2005-04-22  John F. Fay <john.fay.ctr@eglin.af.mil>

	* src/freeglut_menu.c: Yuri D\'Elia\'s changes to get the virtual
	  maximum screen extent instead of the actual screen size.
