2005-02-16  Brian Paul

	* src/freeglut_internal.h, src/freeglut_main.c, src/freeglut_menu.c,
	  src/freeglut_structure.c, src/freeglut_window.c: fixes for menus being
	  attached to multiple buttons/windows (John Fay)
